%N A395383 a(n) = (2*n)! * [x^(2*n)] 1 / cos(x)^5.
%F A395383 a(0) = 1; a(n) = -(1/16) * Sum_{k=0..n-1} (-1)^(n-k) * (10 + 5*9^(n-k) + 25^(n-k)) * binomial(2*n,2*k) * a(k).
